the Santa for nothin'.

455
00:27:03,936 --> 00:27:06,700
- [Grumbling]
- Stupid Santa.

456
00:27:10,208 --> 00:27:12,438
You got some talent, kid.

457
00:27:12,511 --> 00:27:14,809
There's a lot more
to baseball than talent.

458
00:27:14,880 --> 00:27:18,179
Maybe you should have taken some
of that advice in the '81 World Series.

459
00:27:20,686 --> 00:27:22,677
[Chuckles]

460
00:27:22,754 --> 00:27:26,485
I like you, kid.
You got quite the imagination.

461
00:27:26,558 --> 00:27:28,856
'81 World Series, huh?

462
00:27:30,429 --> 00:27:32,556
- You guys see that homer?
- It was pretty good, right?

463
00:27:32,631 --> 00:27:34,792
- Yeah.
- You need to show us how.

464
00:27:34,866 --> 00:27:37,699
<i>- Squints! How's it goin' there, buddy?</i>
- Like you really care.

465
00:27:37,769 --> 00:27:40,135
Just being polite.

466
00:27:42,874 --> 00:27:45,399
<i>EJ., all the way to the fence now.</i>

467
00:27:45,477 --> 00:27:47,638
What are you doing here, Needman?

468
00:27:47,713 --> 00:27:50,341
- Taking some measurements.
- Measurements? For what?

469
00:27:50,415 --> 00:27:52,883
Oh, didn't you hear?
City's putting the sandlot up for sale.

470
00:27:52,951 --> 00:27:56,648
- You can't sell the sandlot.
- Oh, yeah, they can, and I'm buying it.

471
00:27:56,722 --> 00:27:58,485
- Excuse me?
- <i>Face it, Squints.</i>

472
00:27:58,557 --> 00:28:00,752
This old field has run its course.

473
00:28:00,826 --> 00:28:03,727
Besides, there's no real talent
over here nowadays anyway.

474
00:28:03,795 --> 00:28:05,990
Well, you didn't see what I just saw.

475
00:28:06,064 --> 00:28:09,158
Well, I know that I can fetch
a nice price tag...

476
00:28:09,234 --> 00:28:11,998
on some newly developed condos
right where we're standing.

477
00:28:12,070 --> 00:28:15,733
Well, as long as I'm commissioner here,
I don't see that happening.

478
00:28:15,807 --> 00:28:19,766
Yeah? Well, then clean your glasses...

479
00:28:19,845 --> 00:28:23,110
<i>because you got the future</i>
<i>right here, and you don't even see it.</i>

480
00:28:23,181 --> 00:28:25,672
Don't slack that off now!

481
00:28:25,751 --> 00:28:28,413
E. J! Take it all the way
out to the fence.

482
00:28:28,487 --> 00:28:30,478
<i>[Continues, Indistinct]</i>

483
00:28:32,691 --> 00:28:34,784
<i>So, did you have fun playing today?</i>

484
00:28:34,860 --> 00:28:38,762
