but, yeah, I think I did.

485
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:41,025
That's great, sweetie.
I'm glad.

486
00:28:41,099 --> 00:28:43,567
How was your day?
Are you feeling all right?

487
00:28:43,635 --> 00:28:45,694
I'm feeling fine, sweetie.

488
00:28:45,771 --> 00:28:47,762
You're sweet for asking though.

489
00:28:47,839 --> 00:28:50,808
