with my mouth open.

511
00:30:03,748 --> 00:30:06,342
<i>[Two Ton] Oh, I knew I shouldn't</i>
<i>have had that last cheeseburger.</i>

512
00:30:06,418 --> 00:30:08,648
Sometimes you gotta
wait five minutes.

513
00:30:10,522 --> 00:30:13,286
- <i>[Grunting]</i>
- Just relax and let it come out.

514
00:30:15,127 --> 00:30:17,493
- What I do is, I count backwards.
