515
00:30:17,562 --> 00:30:20,053
- Five.
- [Grunting]

516
00:30:20,132 --> 00:30:22,566
Four.

517
00:30:22,634 --> 00:30:25,296
- <i>Ooh.</i>
- Three.

518
00:30:25,370 --> 00:30:27,736
- Two.
- [Moans]

519
00:30:27,806 --> 00:30:29,797
One.

520
00:30:31,443 --> 00:30:34,378
That's it.
I bet you feel better already.

521
00:30:35,447 --> 00:30:37,938
- [Groans]
- [Clamoring]

522
00:30:39,718 --> 00:30:42,380
- <i>[Clattering]</i>
- [Groaning]

523
00:30:42,454 --> 00:30:45,014
- You okay, buddy?
- [Indistinct]

524
00:30:45,090 --> 00:30:47,081
- [Chattering]
- <i>[Thump]</i>

525
00:30:47,159 --> 00:30:49,389
[Chattering]

526
00:30:49,461 --> 00:30:52,862
- <i>[Thumping Continues]</i>
- Did you want to borrow some T. P?

527
00:30:57,335 --> 00:31:00,168
