00:31:16,021 --> 00:31:18,216
- There's only one stall.
- Yeah. One.

532
00:31:18,290 --> 00:31:20,724
We all had to go bad.

533
00:31:20,792 --> 00:31:23,124
You're not gonna rat on us,
are you, Uncle Pork Chop?

534
00:31:23,195 --> 00:31:25,720
Yeah. Yeah, we're not here
to see the movie or anything.

535
00:31:25,797 --> 00:31:28,561
No. We just wanted
to see the new kid.

536
00:31:28,633 --> 00:31:30,931
He's our only shot
at the all-city championship.

537
00:31:31,002 --> 00:31:33,562
- Yeah.
- Relax, boys.

538
00:31:33,638 --> 00:31:35,868
The big Pork Chop
wasn't always a cop.

539
00:31:35,941 --> 00:31:37,932
Besides, it's my night off.

540
00:31:38,009 --> 00:31:41,638
- Oh.
- Just as long as we don't have a situation here.

541
00:31:41,713 --> 00:31:44,079
We're not gonna have
a situation here, are we?

542
00:31:44,149 --> 00:31:46,982
- No.
- Are you sure?

543
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:51,883
Good.
You wait here for my signal.

544
00:31:51,957 --> 00:31:54,653
