Yes!

545
00:31:56,861 --> 00:32:00,126
- Evening, Pork Chop.
- Hey, Casper. Can I get some popcorn?

546
00:32:00,198 --> 00:32:02,132
- You bet.
- Thanks.

547
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:04,725
<i>Here you go. It's fresh.</i>

548
00:32:04,803 --> 00:32:07,966
<i>Good. Oh,</i> Uh...
<i>I'll take a little bit of butter on that.</i>

549
00:32:08,039 --> 00:32:09,734
- Oh, of course.
- Thank you.

550
00:32:09,808 --> 00:32:11,400
- Well, it's topping, but...
- Yeah.

551
00:32:11,476 --> 00:32:13,467
<i>Here it is.</i>
<i>There you are.</i>

552
00:32:13,545 --> 00:32:15,570
- Thank you very much.
- Yeah. Everything okay?

553
00:32:15,647 --> 00:32:18,582
- You seem a bit edgy.
