554
00:32:18,650 --> 00:32:21,619
- Just a little parched. I could do with a Fanta.
- Yeah!

555
00:32:21,686 --> 00:32:23,813
- An orange Fanta, if you have one.
- Yeah, of course.

556
00:32:23,888 --> 00:32:25,913
- Fanta.
- Thanks.

557
00:32:25,991 --> 00:32:28,926
- Here's, uh... here you go.
- Thank you very Much.

558
00:32:28,994 --> 00:32:31,428
That's good. That's good.
I'm feelin' a little peckish though.

559
00:32:31,496 --> 00:32:34,954
- What else can I get for you?
- Listen, can I get some Jujubes too?

560
00:32:35,033 --> 00:32:37,593
- Jujubes comin' up.
- Thanks.

561
00:32:37,669 --> 00:32:39,660
