Go!

562
00:32:39,738 --> 00:32:42,764
- There you go.
- Mm-mmm. Okay, that should just about do it...

563
00:32:42,841 --> 00:32:46,709
except now I need something sweet.

564
00:32:46,778 --> 00:32:48,973
- [Whispering] Goobers.
- <i>Is everything all right?</i>

565
00:32:49,047 --> 00:32:51,311
Yeah, just a little athlete's foot.

566
00:32:51,383 --> 00:32:54,284
<i>[Two Ton Whispering]</i>
<i>Don't open 'em.</i>

567
00:32:54,352 --> 00:32:58,220
- You're one of the good ones, Cassie.
- Okay.

568
00:32:58,290 --> 00:33:00,451
[Electrical Sputtering]

569
00:33:00,525 --> 00:33:03,323
This movie gets funnier
every time I see it.

570
00:33:05,697 --> 00:33:08,495
Psst! Guys, I got 'im.

571
00:33:10,268 --> 00:33:12,361
Hey, Tommy.

572
00:33:16,741 --> 00:33:19,505
Hey, Tommy, Mrs. Santorelli.
How you guys doin'?

573
00:33:19,577 --> 00:33:21,568
What are you guys doing here?

574
00:33:21,646 --> 00:33:24,740
- Stop it.
- What?

575
00:33:24,816 --> 00:33:27,216
Why don't you take your friends
outside so you can talk?

576
00:33:27,285 --> 00:33:29,549
I'll miss the part where
the monster sings and dances.

577
00:33:29,621 --> 00:33:31,646
I love this part.

578
00:33:31,723 --> 00:33:35,022
What do you mean,
the monster sings and dances?

579
00:33:35,093 --> 00:33:37,357
- Nothing. I'll just go.
- <i>[Man Shouting In Movie]</i>

580
00:33:37,429 --> 00:33:40,728
- It's my favorite part.
- You guys, come on.

581
00:33:40,799 --> 00:33:43,359
Excuse me.
Hi, Mrs. Santorelli.

582
00:33:43,435 --> 00:33:46,893
<i>Look, fellas, I appreciate</i>
<i>you asking and everything...</i>

583
00:33:46,971 --> 00:33:49,701
but truth is I have too much
going on in my life right now.

584
00:33:49,774 --> 00:33:51,708
We wouldn't be here
if we didn't need you.

585
00:33:51,776 --> 00:33:55,940
Truth is, we're not exactly
what one would call "good."

586
00:33:56,014 --> 00:33:57,948
I'm sorry, guys. I can't.

587
00:33:58,016 --> 00:34:00,416
- Hey!
- Tommy, I'm only gonna ask you this once...

588
00:34:00,485 --> 00:34:03,010
so I want you to be completely
honest with me, okay?

589
00:34:03,088 --> 00:34:06,057
- Mm-hmm.
- Can you spot me 25 cents for some Goobers?

590
00:34:06,124 --> 00:34:08,285
- God.
- Are you serious?
- <i>Geez Louise.</i>

591
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:12,626
- I only have a nickel.
