592
00:34:12,697 --> 00:34:15,063
What do you got to say for yourself?

593
00:34:15,133 --> 00:34:17,294
We're with him.

594
00:34:17,369 --> 00:34:19,860
- Kill the monster.
- "Kill the monster"?

595
00:34:19,938 --> 00:34:22,236
Kill the monster!

596
00:34:22,307 --> 00:34:25,037
- See ya. Wouldn't wanna be ya.
- Smell ya. Shouldn't have to tell ya.

597
00:34:25,110 --> 00:34:26,407
- Bye, bye.
- Adios.

598
00:34:26,478 --> 00:34:28,810
- [Clamoring]
- Hey, I'm calling the cops.

599
00:34:28,880 --> 00:34:31,576
<i>Hey! Come back here.</i>

600
00:34:31,649 --> 00:34:35,210
<i>Officer Pork Chop, I need you.</i>

601
00:34:35,286 --> 00:34:37,584
<i>Hey, manager,</i>
<i>you can't catch me.</i>

602
00:34:37,655 --> 00:34:40,146
- I see your faces.
- <i>[Boy] Not now.</i>

603
00:34:40,225 --> 00:34:42,716
Where are your parents?

604
00:34:42,794 --> 00:34:45,228
