605
00:34:45,296 --> 00:34:47,662
- Come on, let's go!
- Keep running.

606
00:34:47,732 --> 00:34:50,166
- Excuse me.
- <i>[Boy] Ow! He almost got me.</i>

607
00:34:50,235 --> 00:34:52,430
<i>Come on!</i>

608
00:34:54,172 --> 00:34:56,732
Okay, we're out. We're out.
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

609
00:34:56,808 --> 00:34:58,799
Goobers. Goobers.

610
00:34:58,877 --> 00:35:00,902
- Come on, Two Ton.
- Hey!

611
00:35:00,979 --> 00:35:03,004
I have needs.

612
00:35:04,749 --> 00:35:07,912
I got ya!
Oh, I got ya right there.

613
00:35:07,986 --> 00:35:10,682
Hey, usher guy,
I found my tickets.

614
00:35:15,493 --> 00:35:18,621
There's only two.
What about all the other guys?

615
00:35:18,696 --> 00:35:20,721
What other guys?

616
00:35:22,267 --> 00:35:25,259
Hey! You...

617
00:35:25,503 --> 00:35:27,596
[Whirring]

618
00:35:29,407 --> 00:35:31,432
Whoo.

619
00:35:31,509 --> 00:35:34,342
One chocolate shake comin' up.

620
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:37,939
Why, hello there, sweetie.

621
00:35:38,016 --> 00:35:40,041
[Laughs]
Who are you callin' sweetie, junior?

622
00:35:40,118 --> 00:35:42,143
Just trying to be friendly,
that's all.

623
00:35:42,220 --> 00:35:44,211
All right, little lady-killer...

624
00:35:44,289 --> 00:35:47,281
why don't you lean back
and tell me what you want.

625
00:35:47,358 --> 00:35:50,122
How about a coffee?

626
00:35:50,195 --> 00:35:54,131
A coffee? At your age?
You crack me up, kid.

627
00:35:58,069 --> 00:36:02,699
Here's a cherry Coke.
Kids these days wanna grow up so fast.

628
00:36:08,313 --> 00:36:11,305
What?

629
00:36:11,382 --> 00:36:13,850
Look, I'm not gonna play.

630
00:36:13,918 --> 00:36:17,081
There's just too much going on in my life
right now you just wouldn't understand.

631
00:36:20,658 --> 00:36:22,717
Hit me again?

632
00:36:25,563 --> 00:36:27,724
All right, look.
I might as well tell you.

633
00:36:27,799 --> 00:36:30,666
It's not like you're gonna
go tell anybody, right?

634
00:36:30,735 --> 00:36:33,533
Thanks.

635
00:36:33,605 --> 00:36:37,097
