637
00:36:40,512 --> 00:36:42,673
I was on a box of Wheaties.

638
00:36:42,747 --> 00:36:46,444
I'm gonna be elected
into the Hall of Fame.

639
00:36:46,518 --> 00:36:49,385
Chicks dig me.
Men wanna be me.

640
00:36:49,454 --> 00:36:51,615
That's my real life.

641
00:36:51,689 --> 00:36:53,782
Not this place.

642
00:36:53,858 --> 00:36:56,725
I don't know if this is a dream...

643
00:36:56,794 --> 00:36:58,853
or a second chance...

644
00:36:58,930 --> 00:37:01,023
or what.

645
00:37:01,099 --> 00:37:03,226
I'm gonna enjoy it
for as long as it lasts...

646
00:37:03,301 --> 00:37:06,737
'cause of one reason
and one reason only.

647
00:37:06,804 --> 00:37:09,034
My mom's here.

648
00:37:11,109 --> 00:37:14,704
I'm gonna spend as much time
with her as possible.

649
00:37:14,779 --> 00:37:17,373
I knew you'd understand.

650
00:37:21,386 --> 00:37:23,946
Hey, Ryan?

651
00:37:24,022 --> 00:37:26,957
Thanks for listening, buddy.

652
00:37:28,459 --> 00:37:31,292
